reviews.content: I’m currently on iOS 12.4, on a iPhone 8, and jailbroken with Unc0ver 4.2.1 and I cannot understate how essential the PhotoManager tweak is for jailbreaking iOS users! Have used it since iOS 12.1.4 and I can’t live without it!
Best tweak for doing stuff with photo albums
Works great just a few little bugs but nothing serious.
Latest update not working on A12 12.1.2, when open the camera it crashes. After disabling it the tweak started working.
Tweak worked fine on my i8, 13.6.1 once, but now moving pictures to a user album doesn’t work, it only copies it. Both devices (SE2 and 8) are affected.
